grow

public void grow()
This method adds one block to the snake's body. It temporarily houses the new block in the same location as the snake's 'tail'. During the next iteration of actionPerformed(), the for loop will shift all locations by one, and the new block (now the 'tail') will be in the location as the snake's previous tail.
